      <title>Fireside Chat &amp; Mixer with Karine Jean-Pierre at Miner Building (Myrtilla Miner Building- School of Education)</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/52709977040978/huge/574ff8a81dc420b5180e3c997158b78f375ef786.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Mon, 27 Apr 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>From the White House podium to Howard’s campus, Joshua Olatubosun and Risav Ganguly invite you to an exclusive fireside chat and mixer with Karine Jean-Pierre — the first Black woman and the first openly queer individual to serve as White House Press Secretary.</p>

